{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Divinastros is a roguelike deck builder focused on making massive scores with your cards! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/Divinastros_-_Virgo_Focused.gif?t=1736895475\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick your cards and make combinations with Tarot Cards and the Zodiac to achieve the best build possible! Fight Greek beasts and Gods, meet different characters, uncover new Tarot Decks and make your way to Mount Olimpus. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/Divinastros_-_Bosses.gif?t=1736895475\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every run is unique! Adapt your gameplay to the different Zodiac Signs and beat the many bosses that'll try to stop you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/Divinastros_-_Tarot_Focused.gif?t=1736895475\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet various friendly mythological creatures and characters. Each one of them offers you their help and new Quests to complete!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/Divinastros_-_Choice.gif?t=1736895475\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- 88 Unique Major Arcana Tarot Cards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- 12 Zodiac Signs, each one with their unique gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- 8 Invocations</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- 4 Different Tarot Decks</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736895475","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736895475","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstati